# textdomain: mcl_observers
Observer=Opazovalec
Emits redstone pulse when block in front changes=Odda impulz rdečega kamna, ko se blok spredaj spremeni

An observer is a redstone component which observes the block in front of it and sends a very short redstone pulse whenever this block changes.=Opazovalec je komponenta rdečega kamna, ki opazuje blok pred seboj in pošlje zelo kratek impulz rdečega kamna, kadar koli se ta blok spremeni.

Place the observer directly in front of the block you want to observe with the “face” looking at the block. The arrow points to the side of the output, which is at the opposite side of the “face”. You can place your redstone dust or any other component here.=Postavite opazovalca neposredno pred blok, ki ga želite opazovati, tako da je njegov »obraz« obrnjen proti bloku. Puščica kaže na stran izhoda, ki je na nasprotni strani »obraza«. Tukaj lahko postavite svoj prah rdečega kamna ali katero koli drugo komponento.